{"tid":272754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(一拳超人)  掟鏢爭執　男子涉一拳殺人","createTime":"2017-06-06T05:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T05:27:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a1e32a57781144378af63369ecbb4fb2e889be","tid":272754,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20046227&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20046227%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170606&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=376053aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20046227%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170606&h=bb16483d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20046227&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170606</a><br />\n<br />\n掟鏢爭執　男子涉一拳殺人<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告容定樑昨否認一項誤殺罪受審。<br />\n楊思雅攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】三名飛鏢迷凌晨在酒吧比賽掟鏢，其間因比賽罰則等問題起爭執並動武，其中一名男子揮拳將另一人毆暈，導致對方腦出血，翌日證實死亡。<br />\n男子事後被控一項誤殺罪，昨在高院受審。閉路電視顯示死者曾以骰盅從後偷襲被告，辯方又指死者友人曾向被告揚言「打死你，出唔到呢個門口」，並將點着的香煙掟向被告。<br />\n<br />\n辯稱自衞還擊<br />\n<br />\n被告容定樑（42歲）否認非法殺害男子張顯輝（43歲）。控方表示，被告辯稱自衞還擊，但閉路電視拍下他受襲後先與死者口角，之後他是在雙方沒有身體接觸的情況下忽然揮拳打向死者左頸，死者隨即倒下昏迷，送院期間一度沒呼吸和脈搏，翌日死亡。控方認為被告心存怨恨，伺機揮拳教訓對方。<br />\n死者友人譚柏濠供稱前年8月18日凌晨在何文田一酒吧內與死者及被告比賽掟鏢，他不滿被告將懲罰定得太重而與他起爭執。<br />\n辯方盤問譚，指爭執期間譚曾取笑被告「成日怕輸，成日賴皮，又唔飲罰酒」，當時被告否認，並反駁「你話我（飛）鏢屎，嚟緊硬鏢賽，睇吓邊個攞得獎多」，譚因而不滿被告態度囂張，揚言要打死被告。但譚稱當晚曾飲了兩支威士忌溝蘇打，且事隔太耐，無法記起雙方爭吵內容。聆訊今續。<br />\n案件編號：HCCC83/16<br />\n■記者楊思雅<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ef206fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"a5db8e69771291e0959e02c18d583cc8b64918d6","tid":272754,"uid":59639,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"飲大2 杯屎水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下半世人玩完"},{"pid":"6dd8a827a05f13d133a09fd97ea622c8aee77d24","tid":272754,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5744cdb89f5e03d516444b7becbb286628db7dd","tid":272754,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b695e5619b4d4be29244ffb576f8720e7ac9ce3","tid":272754,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"sonic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3675c52871b72df9b98edf191b1fa4be2b33706d","tid":272754,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"真係一拳超人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e112032fb2da5e53db2933c5504961d23f217c","tid":272754,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打完人又唔敢認<br />\n<br />\n成4X歲人都咁ON9   贏晒又點<br />\n<br />\n出番酒吧咪又係普通人一個  掟鏢呢D原本就係娛樂下  咁認真把撚咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打世界賽咩   國際性比賽都唔知有冇掟鏢玩</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有 搞左好多年<br />\n前兩日先打完世界盃"},{"pid":"e87e86ece8e1cda707b7cdde2d34772979bedec9","tid":272754,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"近日隻抽案例十分多"},{"pid":"c3f67fa9650b1f3ea2a0c8b13b167d5f351bf60f","tid":272754,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"One punch！！！"},{"pid":"b4af9c6639f1407a1ef19e32c30502e4e81fcd9f","tid":272754,"u